{"tha-ap523:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap523:0.2":"Tinadayakavagga ","tha-ap523:0.3":"Tinamutthidayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap523:1.1":"â€œHimavantassavidure, ","tha-ap523:1.2":"lambako nama pabbato; ","tha-ap523:1.3":"Tattheva tisso sambuddho, ","tha-ap523:1.4":"abbhokasamhi cankami. ","tha-ap523:2.1":"Migaluddo pure asim, ","tha-ap523:2.2":"aranne kanane aham; ","tha-ap523:2.3":"Disvana tam devadevam, ","tha-ap523:2.4":"tinamutthimadasaham. ","tha-ap523:3.1":"Nisidanattham buddhassa, ","tha-ap523:3.2":"datva cittam pasadayim; ","tha-ap523:3.3":"Sambuddham abhivadetva, ","tha-ap523:3.4":"pakkamim uttaramukho. ","tha-ap523:4.1":"Aciram gatamattassa, ","tha-ap523:4.2":"migaraja apothayi; ","tha-ap523:4.3":"Sihena pothito santo, ","tha-ap523:4.4":"tattha kalankato aham. ","tha-ap523:5.1":"Asanne me katam kammam, ","tha-ap523:5.2":"buddhasetthe anasave; ","tha-ap523:5.3":"Sumutto saravegova, ","tha-ap523:5.4":"devalokamaganchaham. ","tha-ap523:6.1":"Yupo tattha subho asi, ","tha-ap523:6.2":"punnakammabhinimmito; ","tha-ap523:6.3":"Sahassakando satabhendu, ","tha-ap523:6.4":"dhajalu haritamayo. ","tha-ap523:7.1":"Pabha niddhavate tassa, ","tha-ap523:7.2":"sataramsiva uggato; ","tha-ap523:7.3":"Akinno devakannahi, ","tha-ap523:7.4":"amodim kamakamiham. ","tha-ap523:8.1":"Devaloka cavitvana, ","tha-ap523:8.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap523:8.3":"Agantvana manussattam, ","tha-ap523:8.4":"pattomhi asavakkhayam. ","tha-ap523:9.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap523:9.2":"nisidanamadasaham; ","tha-ap523:9.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap523:9.4":"tinamutthe idam phalam. ","tha-ap523:10.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap523:10.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap523:10.3":"Nagova bandhanam chetva, ","tha-ap523:10.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap523:11.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap523:11.2":"mama buddhassa santike; ","tha-ap523:11.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","tha-ap523:11.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap523:12.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap523:12.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap523:12.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap523:12.4":"katam buddhassa sasanamâ€. ","tha-ap523:13.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma tinamutthidayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap523:14.1":"Tinamutthidayakattherassapadanam pathamam. "}